{"tid":202569,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃秋生驚悚片收山作】《失眠》The Sleep Curse","createTime":"2017-04-15T15:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T07:41:23.000Z","uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"411cd4024fa9e7bce00ee4e86aaf11870d27ccb3","tid":202569,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"預告片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vu08Xey-Rec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvu08Xey-Rec&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=2599c61d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vu08Xey-Rec</a><br />\n<br />\n黃秋生短訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OEfgGj3P8DY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOEfgGj3P8DY&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=f7b7e5c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OEfgGj3P8DY</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------<br />\n**邱禮濤導演及影帝黃秋生相隔20年再度合作血腥極品**<br />\n**挑戰《八仙飯店之人肉叉燒飽》及《伊波拉病毒》大膽尺度**<br />\n**第19屆烏甸尼遠東電影節**<br />\n**4月香港國際電影節上映一刀不剪血淋淋版本**<br />\n**5月正式上映‧全港血肉橫飛!!**<br />\n<br />\n《失眠》(The Sleep Curse)故事大綱<br />\n<br />\n著名大學醫學院教授林惜家（黃秋生　飾），專門研究人類可以長時間不需睡眠的方法。一天，前女友丘夢熙（吳俐璇　飾）突然現身求助，原來她的家人全部患上失眠症，病情去到末期，病人更會陷入失常狀態、極具攻擊性！為探究真相，林惜家開始連串恐怖實驗：潛入停屍間偷取病人大腦，又把丘夢熙關在密室軟禁，藉此研究睡眠和大腦蛋白質之間的關係&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n隨著實驗愈深入，蹊蹺的事情不斷在丘夢熙身上發生；就連林惜家也看似受感染，心底開始出現吃人肉的慾望&hellip; 原來一切牽涉到45年前，孿生姐妹侯文媛和侯文禎（衛詩雅　分飾）的一宗倫常慘案有關！<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n導演：邱禮濤<br />\n編劇：李敏<br />\n領銜主演：黃秋生<br />\n主演：衛詩雅、吳俐璇、麥子樂、船木一輝<br />\n友情演出：林家棟<br />\n<br />\n級別：III<br />\n片長：101.15分鐘<br />\n上映日：2017年5月<br />\n發行：英皇電影<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://www.emp.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.emp.hk&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=136fe08a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.emp.hk</a><br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/EmperorMotionPictures\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEmperorMotionPictures&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=1ff6b378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/EmperorMotionPictures</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/%E5%A4%B1%E7%9C%A0-The-Sleep-Curse-272774649794583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%259C%25A0-The-Sleep-Curse-272774649794583&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=9cbb4dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/%E5%A4%B1%E7%9C%A0-The-Sleep-Curse-272774649794583</a><br />\n<br />\n今次玩切jer 同 揭面皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c290d9361797261b63239d24306d82db7880cda6","tid":202569,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:54:24.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35b34eeaf77ec03ad62a1c606829624c93bc6e3","tid":202569,"uid":62504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:12:47.000Z","msg":"有殺冇賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1989e2adce1a8a29d4df1297fa53550ffcf7ddf3","tid":202569,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"星期一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ntrailer果凌對住鏡頭一野劈落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39bdc0a838fb58748d643dc63ea319a1d9d73efd","tid":202569,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:13:49.000Z","msg":"星期一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc56d42f1c453fedc307da3152fa54a096a1b63","tid":202569,"uid":35221,"